                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18240218-124-off689 t18240218-124-crimeloc692"></join>. On the 31st December, the prisoner came to my house in great distress - I supported her for three weeks - she slept with me. On the 20th of January, about nine o'clock in the morning, I went out leaving her in the house - returned about twelve o'clock, and she was gone - I missed the property stated in the indictment, and much more.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18240218-124-person1207">
                  JOHN 
                  VERGO BUCKLAND
