                  </persName>
            . I am an officer. On the 21st of January, I apprehended the prisoner, and found a gown, whittle, frill and handkerchief on her person - I afterwards went to Dodd's, and got more things.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18240218-124-person1208">
