            . I live in Portland-street. On the 21st January the prisoner applied to me for a lodging, and left a bundle at my house, which I gave to Buckland.</p>
               <p>(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. She was in the habit of lending me things, and I took the liberty to use them.</p>
               <p>PROSECUTRIX. I lent her none of them.</p>
               <p>GUILTY. Aged 31.</p>
